1
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:32,980
=The Secret of the Lost Pearl=

2
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:34,940
=Episode 21=
(Fiction. Do not imitate.)

3
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:41,070
What are they talking about? So serious.

4
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:45,120
How should I know?

5
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:47,600
Chen,

6
00:00:48,110 --> 00:00:49,640
you've been silent here for a while.

7
00:00:49,880 --> 00:00:50,920
What are you thinking?

8
00:00:53,110 --> 00:00:54,790
I'm wondering if that pearl

9
00:00:54,790 --> 00:00:56,560
is what Bai Lingling's boss
is looking for.

10
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:58,790
It makes sense.

11
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:00,122
Otherwise, that foolish girl

12
00:01:00,133 --> 00:01:01,750
wouldn't risk her life

13
00:01:01,750 --> 00:01:03,200
to take on that thing alone.

14
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:05,040
Foolish girl?

15
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,840
I think you're the foolish one.

16
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,046
Who are you talking about?

17
00:01:09,590 --> 00:01:10,590
I'm talking about you.

18
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,480
She's not foolish.

19
00:01:12,590 --> 00:01:13,950
If she weren't hurt,

20
00:01:14,070 --> 00:01:15,640
she'd have run off with the pearl.

21
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,600
Shut up.

22
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:17,440
I'm telling you.

23
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:19,000
Bai Lingling isn't that kind of person.

24
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,400
You just like her.

25
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:21,480
What kind of person is she?

26
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,120
Lu Di, we need to figure out

27
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,840
how to get that pearl,

28
00:01:25,230 --> 00:01:26,430
not argue.

29
00:01:26,430 --> 00:01:27,920
Is she one of us?

30
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:29,590
Is she?

31
00:01:29,590 --> 00:01:30,680
No matter what you say,

32
00:01:30,710 --> 00:01:31,950
I treat her as one of us.

33
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:33,560
Does she treat you the same?

34
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,760
Stop with the nonsense.

35
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:36,040
Why argue now?

36
00:01:36,353 --> 00:01:37,459
It's not the time for that.

37
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,120
Youxi, he's bullying me.

38
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,280
I should strangle you.

39
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,400
I can't breathe.

40
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,760
Enough.

41
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,680
Why did we encounter such a thing?

42
00:02:09,470 --> 00:02:10,310
Chen,

43
00:02:10,590 --> 00:02:12,030
what is

44
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:13,280
this ghost-face giant spider?

45
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:15,400
It's a branch of spiders,

46
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:17,396
with markings that look
like a human face,

47
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:19,190
also called the Ghost-Face Spider.

48
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:21,003
I saw one once in the Kunlun Mountains.

49
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:24,030
We were working in a canyon;

50
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,590
our comrades disappeared mysteriously.

51
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,560
At the canyon's depths,

52
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,520
we found a huge spider nest,

53
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,430
and our friends' corpses

54
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,120
turned into dry tree bark.

55
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:39,590
That's creepy.

56
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:43,800
Chen, don't spiders live in darkness

57
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,960
with poor eyesight,

58
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:46,840
using webs and touch

59
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:48,560
to hunt?

60
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,710
I didn't see any web in the dark.

61
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:51,870
It came straight for me.

62
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:52,800
What's going on?

63
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:55,080
Judging by its attack,

64
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,470
it's like a tarantula,

65
00:02:57,190 --> 00:02:58,840
hunting by smell.

66
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:02,150
So, it hunts by scent?

67
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:04,560
Chen,

68
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:07,560
that pearl must be precious.

69
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:08,710
Think about it.

70
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:11,240
Having a giant spider guard it

71
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,750
means it's very important.

72
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,120
No pearl is worth risking our lives for.

73
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,120
Chen,

74
00:03:16,150 --> 00:03:18,240
fighting it means death.

75
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,280
Let's retreat.

76
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:20,400
Retreat?

77
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:22,840
If we retreat now,
all our earlier efforts are wasted.

78
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:25,590
Better to preserve ourselves for later.

79
00:03:25,710 --> 00:03:27,120
Lu Di...

80
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:45,360
Miss Bai, Ms. He,

81
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,120
stay put!

82
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,630
Hurry!

83
00:03:58,870 --> 00:03:59,710
Idiot, hurry!

84
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,300
Run, Lu!

85
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:11,150
Hurry up!

86
00:04:16,830 --> 00:04:18,430
That jerk is above us!

87
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,560
Chen, what do we do?

88
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,630
Which way now?

89
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,750
Split into two.

90
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:27,120
Chubby, take Lu.

91
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:28,360
I'll distract it.

92
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,200
- Okay.
- Go.

93
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:30,270
Go, Lu.

94
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:35,880
Lu, this way.

95
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,360
It's supposed to leave.

96
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,750
Why did it come this way?

97
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:56,960
Hurry.

98
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,080
Go, Lu.

99
00:04:58,310 --> 00:04:59,150
Hide here.

100
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:03,560
Lu, be careful.

101
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,400
Stay put.

102
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,270
I'll lure it away, okay?

103
00:05:06,310 --> 00:05:07,390
Be careful.

104
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:10,600
Jerk, I'm here.

105
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:34,070
Chubby, the spider's coming for me!

106
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,110
Lu!

107
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:43,360
Jerk, I'm here.

108
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,750
Come get me!

109
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,110
Chen.

110
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,270
Are you okay, Lu?

111
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,430
How am I okay?

112
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:02,360
You lured it straight to me.

113
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,800
Why is it only after Lu?

114
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,750
How would I know?

115
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:08,430
What's special about Lu?

116
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:09,750
What's special?

117
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,510
He has a gold tooth.

118
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,390
Right, Lu.

119
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,040
Close your mouth!

120
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:17,480
It's your tooth flashing!

121
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,160
My gold tooth?

122
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:27,750
I closed it.

123
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:29,510
It's still clawing at me.

124
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:34,390
Does this spider think
Lu is Tang Sanzang?

125
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:35,240
So obsessive.

126
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,750
Is his meat that fragrant?

127
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:38,670
What's fragrant?

128
00:06:40,510 --> 00:06:41,360
The Wenxiang Jade?

129
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,870
Lu, cover your Wenxiang Jade.

130
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:45,960
The Wenxiang Jade?

131
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,560
Oh, my god.

132
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:29,150
Lu!

133
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,000
Lu!

134
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:34,540
- Lu!
- Come.

135
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,720
What happened?

136
00:07:37,270 --> 00:07:39,560
A 1,000 obstacle race.

137
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,400
Let me tell you.

138
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:43,510
Luckily, Chen reacted fast.

139
00:07:43,950 --> 00:07:46,480
Otherwise, Lu would've been

140
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:47,950
the spider's dinner.

141
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:50,920
Chen, you saved my life again.

142
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:52,390
Thanks.

143
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:56,480
That jade causes trouble.

144
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:59,630
Who knew the spider liked it?

145
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:00,800
The Wenxiang Jade?

146
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:03,720
So, the spider

147
00:08:03,870 --> 00:08:05,190
was drawn out by the jade?

148
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,630
Exactly.

149
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:09,480
With the beast guarding the pearl,

150
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,390
we probably can't get it.

151
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,750
Pearl?

152
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,486
Do you have a death wish?

153
00:08:15,070 --> 00:08:16,000
I have a plan.

154
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,510
Give me the jade.

155
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,880
Let's go.

156
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,000
Again?

157
00:08:33,670 --> 00:08:34,510
What are you doing?

158
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,080
It's coming out.

159
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:54,600
Hurry!

160
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,440
- Retreat.
- Go.

161
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:31,150
Why hasn't it come?

162
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:32,470
Why the rush?

163
00:09:33,150 --> 00:09:33,990
Wait.

164
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,510
Why does it stop there?

165
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:14,390
Has it noticed our ambush?

166
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:18,440
This thousand-year-old spider
is different.

167
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,360
It's enlightened.

168
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:22,080
It got hit!

169
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,960
So precise.

170
00:11:58,750 --> 00:11:59,590
Let's go.

171
00:12:17,030 --> 00:12:18,390
What exactly is that thing?

172
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,030
It can move on its own.

173
00:12:20,270 --> 00:12:21,110
Go.

174
00:12:22,270 --> 00:12:23,200
Go, go.

175
00:12:29,790 --> 00:12:30,630
Chubby,

176
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:31,750
look!

177
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,720
Oh, my god.

178
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,440
So beautiful.

179
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:37,020
Lu,

180
00:12:37,030 --> 00:12:37,870
check it out.

181
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,600
How much is this worth?

182
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:40,910
Hard to say.

183
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,320
I know

184
00:12:42,550 --> 00:12:45,630
that Cixi had a pearl in her mouth.

185
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,160
It was this big.

186
00:12:47,170 --> 00:12:48,030
This big.

187
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:51,790
It was worth over 10 million taels
of silver.

188
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:56,080
This one is better in quality,

189
00:12:56,550 --> 00:12:57,480
bigger,

190
00:12:57,790 --> 00:12:59,720
and flashes red.

191
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:01,550
Chen,

192
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,600
just for this,

193
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,080
I forgive you for not letting me

194
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,030
touch the burial items.

195
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,080
I guess this pearl

196
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:12,080
is similar

197
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,720
to what Chen Youxi handled

198
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,080
in the Nether Ruins.

199
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,120
How do you know?

200
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,510
I'm here on orders.

201
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:20,150
I know what the item that cursed you

202
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,320
looks like.

203
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:23,030
Also, I know this pearl

204
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,790
is called the Lingxiao Pearl.

205
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:27,960
Are you saying

206
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,750
anyone who touches it

207
00:13:29,790 --> 00:13:31,120
will be cursed?

208
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:35,630
That's eerie.

209
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:37,403
Whoever touches it gets unlucky.

210
00:13:38,550 --> 00:13:39,390
Look.

211
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:42,480
The base has eight animal heads carved,

212
00:13:42,670 --> 00:13:44,240
each representing a trigram:

213
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:47,080
Qian is horse, Kun is ox,

214
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:49,870
Zhen is dragon, Xun is chicken,

215
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:52,200
Kan is pig, Li is pheasant,

216
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:54,790
Gen is dog, and Dui is sheep.

217
00:13:55,030 --> 00:13:57,440
The top four and bottom four

218
00:13:57,670 --> 00:14:00,510
form a 3D Bagua.

219
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,080
What does that mean?

220
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,670
I've been thinking all along.

221
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,270
If the Bagua array Bai Lingling

222
00:14:08,270 --> 00:14:09,240
and I fell into

223
00:14:09,630 --> 00:14:11,240
were just a mechanism,

224
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:13,100
it wouldn't need to be so complex.

225
00:14:13,100 --> 00:14:14,320
(Qian, Kun, Kan, Li, Zhen, Gen)

226
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:15,840
Until I saw this container.

227
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:19,870
When I saw the Lingxiao Pearl,

228
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,240
I realized

229
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,910
maybe the entire princess tomb

230
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,360
is a massive Bagua array.

231
00:14:28,150 --> 00:14:29,120
The Lingxiao Pearl cave

232
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:31,150
we're in

233
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:32,670
is the center of the array.

234
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,150
That means every hall

235
00:14:35,390 --> 00:14:37,270
we've walked through

236
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:39,000
is a trigram.

237
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:40,910
Exactly.

238
00:14:41,390 --> 00:14:42,790
If there are four trigrams above,

239
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:43,840
they'll be the giant face,

240
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:46,116
(Soul-locking stair)
the stairs, the fake main hall,

241
00:14:46,127 --> 00:14:47,949
(Pearl Cave)
and the chamber Huang destroyed.

242
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:49,133
(Bagua array)
The bottom four

243
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:50,750
are the Bagua array,

244
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:53,030
Bell Hall, Hidden Spring,

245
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,840
and the princess's true main hall.

246
00:14:58,240 --> 00:15:00,790
Now, we're missing just one:

247
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:03,960
the true main hall.

248
00:15:04,650 --> 00:15:05,500
Wait.

249
00:15:05,510 --> 00:15:07,270
This is dizzying.

250
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:10,270
I can understand

251
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:11,670
that the Bagua array is below,

252
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:13,440
but why are Bell Hall and others

253
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:15,720
on the same plane?

254
00:15:16,390 --> 00:15:17,600
Think of it this way:

255
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:20,840
The tunnels have ups and downs

256
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:22,000
to make us

257
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,080
feel elevation.

258
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,480
You think you're high,

259
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:27,200
but actually low.

260
00:15:29,030 --> 00:15:30,000
Chen is right.

261
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:32,600
It's like the soul-locking stair.

262
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:33,800
Right?

263
00:15:34,030 --> 00:15:36,600
The main hall is a cave; the pit is Kan.

264
00:15:37,790 --> 00:15:39,910
Its position in the array

265
00:15:40,750 --> 00:15:41,630
should be northeast.

266
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:45,000
The compass pointer went crazy

267
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:45,960
since we entered.

268
00:15:46,270 --> 00:15:47,270
It never worked.

269
00:15:47,670 --> 00:15:48,840
Based on the tomb layout

270
00:15:48,840 --> 00:15:50,120
we passed,

271
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:53,080
northeast should be...

272
00:15:53,910 --> 00:15:54,790
Where?

273
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,510
There.

274
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:58,990
What are you doing?

275
00:16:14,300 --> 00:16:15,660
(Xiangmu, Princess Xian'an)

276
00:16:25,090 --> 00:16:28,190
♪A tiny ark sails;
the sky opens its eyes♪

277
00:16:29,870 --> 00:16:33,550
♪Stillness in motion,
the earth plays its chord♪

278
00:16:34,610 --> 00:16:39,190
♪A leaf falls;
we cross through time and space♪

279
00:16:39,340 --> 00:16:46,340
♪In a blink, all things rest
upon our hands♪

280
00:16:46,900 --> 00:16:57,920
♪La la♪

281
00:17:04,670 --> 00:17:06,660
♪No line divides the border♪

282
00:17:07,100 --> 00:17:09,440
♪Nothing limits your performance♪

283
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:11,810
♪Everything shows perfect harmony♪

284
00:17:11,810 --> 00:17:14,500
♪Love circles the sky,
the earth, and our faith♪

285
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:17,710
♪Hey hey hey♪

286
00:17:19,040 --> 00:17:20,860
♪Hey hey hey♪

287
00:17:23,510 --> 00:17:24,510
♪Hey hey♪

288
00:17:24,660 --> 00:17:25,660
♪Hey hey♪

289
00:17:27,120 --> 00:17:28,200
♪Hey hey♪

290
00:17:29,830 --> 00:17:34,030
♪Step into the galaxy of colors♪

291
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:38,330
♪Stars connect our hearts as one♪

292
00:17:40,610 --> 00:17:42,830
